<div class="card settings-section" id="resendSection"><div class="card-header">Resend API 配置</div><div class="card-body"><div class="form-group"><label class="form-label">API Key</label><input type="password" name="resend_api_key" class="form-input" value="" placeholder="{{ settings.resend_api_key is defined and settings.resend_api_key ? '已设置（留空保留原值）' : '请输入 Resend API Key' }}">{% if settings.resend_api_key is defined and settings.resend_api_key %}<p class="form-hint">API Key 已保存，留空提交将保留当前值</p>{% elseif resend_api_key is defined and resend_api_key %}<p class="form-hint">当前使用 config.php 中的默认值</p>{% endif %}</div><div class="info-block" style="font-size:0.85rem;"><strong>使用说明：</strong><br>1. 注册 <a href="https://resend.com" target="_blank" style="color:var(--accent-purple);">resend.com</a> 账号<br>2. 添加并验证域名（添加 DNS 记录）<br>3. 创建 API Key 填入上方<br>4. 发件人邮箱域名需与 Resend 中验证的域名一致</div></div></div>
